description:
Animal's Super Senses - Episode 9: The Sky | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'Animal's Super Senses - Episode 10' here: https://youtu.be/AGCV-nJfdqg

Animals that live life on the wing, have a vast expanse of sky to navigate, find mates, locate food, and avoid predators in… Living in this aerial realm requires a unique set of senses, specialised to cope with life above ground…
In this episode of Super Senses, we find out more about when senses take flight… and animals become masters of the sky!  The speed and precision of a bird of prey captures our attention…and leaves us awestruck.

You will see fascinating shots from the deep seas and up in the air, capturing great stories and pictures from everything our beautiful and interesting planet has to offer. 

Enjoy stories about nature, wildlife, culture, people, history and more to come.
